{"tid":1802833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.27光復元朗銀髮婆婆與防暴警對峙 入圍具代表女性抗爭者","createTime":"2019-12-29T18:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T17:08:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b2b2434de7d3b8ad170b956e204c789a372d14","tid":1802833,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191229/large/1577606142_91b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577606142_91b1.jpg&h=6543000a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年全球多個地方出現抗爭浪潮，海外媒體《Indiatimes》選出36幅最具代表女性抗爭者的照片，其中本港7.27光復元朗遊行中，一名手無寸鐵的銀髮婆婆在抗爭前線與防暴警對峙的照片被選中，與智利、巴西、南韓等多國為民主、為公義、為反抗政府惡法的女示威者同入圍。<br />\n<br />\n7.27元朗遊行當日，警方在大馬路一帶施放催淚彈，其後與市民對峙。其間該名手持拐杖、毫無裝備的銀髮婆婆突然衝出來，站在防暴警與市民之間，並勸喻市民離開：「你哋快啲走啦！」她又張開四肢，「大」字型擋在市民前面，在場市民則勸婆婆離開現場，但婆婆則表示要一齊走。眾人後來一起後退。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428552&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK91lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=12758ce8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428552&h=a0a2c7d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428552</a>"},{"pid":"62de2f70c186fb0cacc71e76dc1dc0044a4c1f95","tid":1802833,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b2b2434de7d3b8ad170b956e204c789a372d14","tid":1802833,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191229/large/1577606142_91b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577606